name: Canadian Banc Corp. Preferred Shares
longDescription: Canadian Banc Corp is a Canadian-based company operating in the financial services sector. It is a mutual fund corporation that invests primarily in a portfolio of common shares of the Canadian chartered banks including Toronto-Dominion Bank, Bank of Nova Scotia, Canadian Imperial Bank of Commerce, Royal Bank of Canada, Bank of Montreal, and National Bank of Canada. Its investment objective is to pay monthly cash dividends.
